WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.600
[Disclaimer:
All depicted events are fictional

00:00:02.640 --> 00:00:05.240
and for entertainment purposes only;
viewer discretion is advised]

00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:34.920
Khem!

00:00:35.800 --> 00:00:37.000
I'm sorry, Jet,

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:38.640
but I can't bear losing anyone again.

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:39.800
We're coming with you, then.

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:42.880
Khem's birthday is in seven days.

00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:44.120
If he makes it until then,

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:45.280
the curse will be lifted.

00:00:45.320 --> 00:00:47.520
Are you sure you can handle this

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:48.920
without your master?

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:51.080
He's already lost so much for me.

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:52.880
- Khemjira must survive!
- Khemjira must survive!

00:00:58.120 --> 00:00:59.120
Khem,

00:00:59.160 --> 00:01:00.440
don't give up yet.

00:01:03.580 --> 00:01:04.459
Let go!

00:01:05.440 --> 00:01:06.450
Let go of me!

00:01:07.680 --> 00:01:08.440
Hey!

00:02:09.180 --> 00:02:10.479
You finally showed up, Mr. Fancy-pants.

00:02:10.940 --> 00:02:13.360
Thought you'd let your buddy
get his ass kicked,

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:14.210
huh?

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:16.660
Let my bro go.

00:02:17.340 --> 00:02:18.760
If you wanna blame someone, blame me.

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:20.329
You both are pieces of shit.

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:23.970
If you hadn't poked your nose
into our turf,

00:02:24.770 --> 00:02:26.050
the girls wouldn't have dumped me.

00:02:26.780 --> 00:02:27.660
And even my girl,

00:02:28.240 --> 00:02:29.840
Khaopad, dumped me!

00:02:31.180 --> 00:02:33.200
With that ugly mug of yours,

00:02:33.620 --> 00:02:35.860
whether it's Khaopad,
Khaosuay, or Khaoniew,

00:02:36.460 --> 00:02:38.500
no girl's gonna pick you, dude.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:39.800
You've got a smart mouth, huh?

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:42.280
Hey!

00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:49.220
My bro!

00:02:51.150 --> 00:02:52.530
Kachen, my buddy,

00:02:52.570 --> 00:02:53.620
run!

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:56.880
What do you want?

00:02:57.410 --> 00:02:58.900
I already broke up with her.

00:02:59.079 --> 00:03:01.160
If you want her,
go ask her out yourself.

00:03:01.980 --> 00:03:02.700
Fuck that.

00:03:03.650 --> 00:03:05.270
Bring that pretty mug over here

00:03:05.310 --> 00:03:07.080
so we can beat it up.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:08.800
You up for it?

00:03:09.170 --> 00:03:10.030
Fine.

00:03:10.540 --> 00:03:12.100
If I win,

00:03:12.390 --> 00:03:13.860
let my buddy go.

00:03:16.370 --> 00:03:17.130
No!

00:03:17.380 --> 00:03:18.640
My buddy,

00:03:18.810 --> 00:03:20.400
don't do that!

00:03:20.710 --> 00:03:22.220
Don't stop me, Paran.

00:03:23.810 --> 00:03:25.200
Just think of it

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:26.560
as me paying for the sin

00:03:27.160 --> 00:03:28.780
of being born this hot.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:35.860
If you're ready to die, bring it on!

00:03:36.740 --> 00:03:38.329
Hey, guys.

00:03:38.600 --> 00:03:39.560
Kachen!

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:41.079
My buddy... No!

00:03:42.079 --> 00:03:43.240
Kachen,

00:03:43.340 --> 00:03:44.810
run!

00:03:44.850 --> 00:03:48.480
No!

00:03:48.880 --> 00:03:49.900
Run.

00:03:49.940 --> 00:03:51.120
Kachen,

00:03:51.160 --> 00:03:54.360
no!

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:56.680
Gosh,

00:03:56.720 --> 00:03:58.300
cut the boasting, Kachen.

00:03:58.740 --> 00:04:00.500
The truth is a hundred times smaller.

00:04:47.020 --> 00:04:48.270
What took you so long?

00:04:50.230 --> 00:04:51.820
I was...

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:56.110
So you handled all of them?

00:05:00.460 --> 00:05:01.230
Yeah.

00:05:03.900 --> 00:05:05.780
Pay the compensation to them for me.

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:19.280
I think...

00:05:19.530 --> 00:05:20.980
you got it all wrong, Jane.

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:23.000
Anyway, guys,

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:26.560
since then, Paran and I

00:05:27.080 --> 00:05:28.520
have become best buddies,

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:31.160
like ride-or-die kind of friends.

00:05:32.480 --> 00:05:33.640
Right, bro?

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:37.680
So,

00:05:38.120 --> 00:05:40.120
you were a thug, Master?

00:05:44.260 --> 00:05:45.620
I only defended myself.

00:05:47.270 --> 00:05:48.590
I've let go of that life.

00:05:52.190 --> 00:05:54.590
Growing up means getting wiser,

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:57.600
not just getting older.

00:06:06.220 --> 00:06:07.310
Come on, man.

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:09.990
Master just said
you need to get wiser, too.

00:06:13.300 --> 00:06:14.380
Jet,

00:06:16.850 --> 00:06:18.170
you know very well...

00:06:18.780 --> 00:06:20.780
my age isn't the only thing
that's bigger.

00:06:22.370 --> 00:06:23.660
You forgot,

00:06:23.700 --> 00:06:24.460
huh?

00:06:27.970 --> 00:06:29.740
Shall we dig up some old memories,

00:06:29.970 --> 00:06:30.830
huh?

00:06:30.870 --> 00:06:31.660
You down?

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:35.840
Hey!

00:06:35.960 --> 00:06:36.920
Quit it.

00:06:37.080 --> 00:06:39.290
Can you stop messing with my brother?

00:06:42.040 --> 00:06:43.120
Enough.

00:06:48.060 --> 00:06:50.180
I called Kachen here today

00:06:51.950 --> 00:06:53.260
because we need him.

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:02.120
Right, Jane.

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:06.600
Are you still putting spells
on your tukata sia kaban?

00:07:10.270 --> 00:07:11.980
Well,

00:07:12.580 --> 00:07:14.720
I do perform some spells,

00:07:14.760 --> 00:07:16.240
but not seriously...

00:07:16.960 --> 00:07:19.130
I treat them as art toys.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:22.520
No need to lie.

00:07:24.760 --> 00:07:25.890
I don't mind it.

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:32.430
We really need them this time.

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:02.800
Ramphueng won't hear anything

00:08:04.440 --> 00:08:06.080
we say in this room.

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:14.320
I'll go over the whole plan just once.

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:16.030
These materials are consecrated.

00:10:18.520 --> 00:10:20.120
Tell me if you need help.

00:10:22.360 --> 00:10:24.680
Get it done as quickly as you can.

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:29.700
I'm made to handle urgent tasks, Master.

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:31.000
I'll make it in time.

00:10:44.580 --> 00:10:45.900
What are you doing, Khem?

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:47.440
You seem dedicated.

00:10:50.820 --> 00:10:51.940
Some keepsakes.

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:56.940
At first, I planned to...

00:10:57.420 --> 00:10:59.020
send a letter to everyone

00:11:00.900 --> 00:11:02.380
so that if I were gone,

00:11:03.640 --> 00:11:05.640
they'd have something to remember me by.

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:13.860
But now,

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:18.440
I'll use this

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:21.520
to remember those who've helped me.

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:46.110
♫Just one glance, and I could feel♫

00:11:46.150 --> 00:11:50.490
♫A vow long hidden, suddenly revealed,♫

00:11:50.530 --> 00:11:54.870
♫Leading our souls in a destined appeal♫

00:11:54.910 --> 00:11:59.100
♫To meet once more with a bond to seal♫

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:07.760
You don't need to
bear all of this alone anymore.

00:12:17.760 --> 00:12:19.840
You need to trust everyone, Khem.

00:12:20.580 --> 00:12:23.780
♫It's more than love at first sight,♫

00:12:23.820 --> 00:12:25.990
♫But a bond through every life♫

00:12:26.030 --> 00:12:29.470
♫Our destinies cross again in this life♫

00:12:29.510 --> 00:12:32.540
♫You'll be my last, my eternal light,♫

00:12:32.580 --> 00:12:34.870
♫From now until the end of time♫

00:12:38.360 --> 00:12:41.440
♫Whether it's a dream or it's true,♫

00:12:41.480 --> 00:12:43.760
♫My heart forever stays with you♫

00:12:43.800 --> 00:12:47.200
♫No force shall tear our souls in two♫

00:12:47.240 --> 00:12:50.530
♫I love you through and through♫

00:12:50.570 --> 00:12:52.700
♫Even if the world ceases to move,♫

00:12:52.740 --> 00:12:55.890
♫These words will still be true,♫

00:12:55.930 --> 00:13:01.050
♫I love you♫

00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:26.800
Whoa, bro.

00:14:26.910 --> 00:14:28.260
That was dope.

00:14:28.720 --> 00:14:29.760
What do you think, Charn?

00:14:29.800 --> 00:14:30.520
Was that dope?

00:14:33.620 --> 00:14:34.500
Yes,

00:14:34.760 --> 00:14:35.400
very...

00:14:37.240 --> 00:14:38.120
Hey.

00:14:39.880 --> 00:14:40.840
Are you okay?

00:14:46.000 --> 00:14:47.690
I think that was too slow.

00:14:48.760 --> 00:14:50.760
To run from that Ramphueng,

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:52.120
we need to be faster.

00:14:59.880 --> 00:15:01.280
I can do it for you if you can't.

00:15:02.340 --> 00:15:03.780
Master said

00:15:03.880 --> 00:15:06.360
this task needs Charn's instincts.

00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:11.840
Don't worry.

00:15:12.490 --> 00:15:14.600
One more round with him
and you'll get used to it.

00:15:20.160 --> 00:15:21.800
You really trust him, don't you?

00:15:23.340 --> 00:15:24.420
If my instincts weren't strong,

00:15:27.510 --> 00:15:29.220
you'd have let him handle it.

00:15:42.560 --> 00:15:43.830
You sure he's got this?

00:15:54.840 --> 00:15:56.240
No matter what, I'm going with him.

00:15:58.960 --> 00:16:00.150
Whoa,

00:16:01.480 --> 00:16:03.800
I've never seen you
trust someone this much.

00:16:09.840 --> 00:16:11.170
Don't bother him too much.

00:16:12.120 --> 00:16:13.400
Just focus on teaching him.

00:16:17.110 --> 00:16:18.110
What, Jane?

00:16:18.720 --> 00:16:19.440
Yeah.

00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:21.480
We're fine.

00:16:30.720 --> 00:16:32.400
How long have you known Jet, Charn?

00:16:36.800 --> 00:16:38.400
We met at the volunteer camp

00:16:39.320 --> 00:16:40.940
a month ago.

00:16:43.800 --> 00:16:44.880
Only a month?

00:16:45.750 --> 00:16:47.750
I've known him since he was 16.

00:16:56.580 --> 00:16:57.540
Oh, yeah?

00:16:59.110 --> 00:17:00.420
He never mentioned you.

00:17:03.510 --> 00:17:04.920
Maybe he's been busy.

00:17:05.800 --> 00:17:08.520
We haven't met
since he went to university.

00:17:13.520 --> 00:17:14.440
Oh, okay.

00:17:15.780 --> 00:17:16.880
If you're really close,

00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:18.720
you'd probably make time to meet.

00:17:21.250 --> 00:17:22.250
We're really close.

00:17:23.050 --> 00:17:25.859
We've been through a lot together,
you know.

00:17:32.250 --> 00:17:33.480
How close...

00:17:33.520 --> 00:17:34.840
are you two, though?

00:17:39.520 --> 00:17:40.760
What do you mean?

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:43.800
Well,

00:17:45.560 --> 00:17:46.960
I got close to him...

00:17:48.560 --> 00:17:50.040
'cause I was his first.

00:17:53.320 --> 00:17:54.200
Well,

00:17:56.100 --> 00:17:57.750
I've never done it with anyone before.

00:18:00.240 --> 00:18:01.240
So...

00:18:01.840 --> 00:18:03.560
I'm your first?

00:18:05.920 --> 00:18:06.720
Obviously.

00:18:17.240 --> 00:18:18.320
You're shocked, huh?

00:18:20.560 --> 00:18:21.750
He didn't tell you, did he?

00:18:26.200 --> 00:18:27.450
If he didn't mention it,

00:18:29.320 --> 00:18:30.800
I probably don't need to know.

00:18:34.960 --> 00:18:35.960
Suit yourself.

00:18:37.840 --> 00:18:40.090
But if you can outpace me today,

00:18:42.880 --> 00:18:44.300
I'll tell you myself.

00:18:50.800 --> 00:18:51.600
Deal?

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:14.880
Get in the car.

00:19:28.940 --> 00:19:30.120
No need to rush.

00:19:33.140 --> 00:19:34.280
We have all afternoon.

00:20:07.200 --> 00:20:09.020
Holy shit!

00:20:09.610 --> 00:20:10.880
That's even faster.

00:21:18.600 --> 00:21:20.040
Shit,

00:21:20.080 --> 00:21:21.540
that was you?

00:21:32.360 --> 00:21:33.240
Charn,

00:21:33.520 --> 00:21:34.600
that was fire!

00:21:39.300 --> 00:21:40.450
Hey, bro.

00:21:40.490 --> 00:21:41.410
You alright?

00:21:42.720 --> 00:21:44.160
Was that your revenge?

00:21:46.440 --> 00:21:47.360
No,

00:21:47.560 --> 00:21:48.280
I was just...

00:21:49.960 --> 00:21:50.680
What?

00:22:13.800 --> 00:22:16.200
I was hoping you'd have a plan.

00:22:19.920 --> 00:22:21.990
Still, I must praise you.

00:22:25.250 --> 00:22:27.250
In so little time,

00:22:28.040 --> 00:22:31.620
you've sealed the trace of his spirit
so completely.

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:38.120
A little retaliation is welcome.

00:22:40.200 --> 00:22:42.600
Don't fail me.

00:22:47.880 --> 00:22:49.400
So that I can enjoy myself...

00:22:59.040 --> 00:23:01.240
Before every last one of you

00:23:01.360 --> 00:23:04.360
gets wiped out tonight.

00:23:12.680 --> 00:23:14.600
I told you
to use a different car, didn't I?

00:23:19.000 --> 00:23:20.880
This won't seat all of us.

00:23:21.200 --> 00:23:23.120
You said you needed it
to run away from that ghost.

00:23:23.720 --> 00:23:25.080
This is the cheapest one.

00:23:26.120 --> 00:23:26.920
Is this...

00:23:27.560 --> 00:23:28.840
the cheapest one?

00:23:30.200 --> 00:23:31.360
That's right, Khem.

00:23:43.980 --> 00:23:45.840
But it's gonna be pretty tight.

00:24:09.440 --> 00:24:10.760
Be careful.

00:24:11.300 --> 00:24:12.760
Don't ever get hurt,

00:24:12.800 --> 00:24:13.680
okay?

00:24:13.840 --> 00:24:14.840
I know.

00:24:15.720 --> 00:24:16.760
Don't worry.

00:24:16.800 --> 00:24:17.840
I'm hard to kill, you know.

00:24:18.840 --> 00:24:19.780
Ouch!

00:24:19.820 --> 00:24:20.650
Hard to kill, huh?

00:24:20.690 --> 00:24:21.680
Come on, Jane.

00:24:22.000 --> 00:24:23.320
Can't you let me be cool for a sec?

00:24:40.200 --> 00:24:41.200
Please protect him.

00:24:42.320 --> 00:24:43.960
He's my only brother.

00:24:48.080 --> 00:24:49.280
You don't need to worry.

00:24:50.760 --> 00:24:53.520
I won't let anything happen to him.

00:24:54.480 --> 00:24:56.080
Don't push yourself too hard, either.

00:25:04.720 --> 00:25:05.720
Are you ready?

00:25:07.040 --> 00:25:07.840
Yes.

00:25:08.640 --> 00:25:09.640
Come with me.

00:25:19.320 --> 00:25:20.800
You sure
you don't wanna know it anymore?

00:25:25.440 --> 00:25:26.280
Yes.

00:25:28.840 --> 00:25:30.720
Whatever his past was,

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:32.640
it doesn't matter to me.

00:25:35.320 --> 00:25:37.360
The only one I care to be with

00:25:39.200 --> 00:25:40.440
is who he is now.

00:25:41.240 --> 00:25:43.240
Whoa,

00:25:43.800 --> 00:25:45.400
you've won my heart, man.

00:25:46.000 --> 00:25:47.000
Hey, Kachen.

00:26:09.600 --> 00:26:10.600
The time has come.

00:26:12.880 --> 00:26:14.560
May you all be safe.

00:26:44.040 --> 00:26:45.200
That's not him.

00:26:57.440 --> 00:26:58.640
Follow them.

00:27:28.080 --> 00:27:29.080
They're here.

00:27:39.840 --> 00:27:41.040
Oh, shit!

00:28:04.960 --> 00:28:07.960
Ramphueng's been growing her power
for over 400 years.

00:28:10.040 --> 00:28:11.560
The closer we get to Khem's birthday,

00:28:13.440 --> 00:28:15.080
the stronger she becomes.

00:28:16.400 --> 00:28:18.960
Even I can't say for certain
that I can stop her.

00:28:21.360 --> 00:28:23.440
But there's one thing on our side,

00:28:25.440 --> 00:28:26.440
and that is time.

00:28:31.640 --> 00:28:33.200
We'll stall her

00:28:33.560 --> 00:28:35.960
and lure her into wasting her strength.

00:28:43.600 --> 00:28:46.000
The curse that binds her to Khem

00:28:46.880 --> 00:28:50.080
lets her sense Khem's soul
no matter where she is.

00:28:53.520 --> 00:28:56.160
I'll enchant Khem's belongings

00:28:57.120 --> 00:28:58.840
and have you all carry them.

00:29:01.720 --> 00:29:04.000
It should confuse her for a while.

00:29:08.080 --> 00:29:10.400
But she won't be fooled for long.

00:29:11.840 --> 00:29:14.640
When she knows, Jane's tukata sia kaban

00:29:15.560 --> 00:29:18.760
will radiate
the strongest trace of Khem's soul.

00:29:21.800 --> 00:29:24.640
Someone will have to stand in
as the false Khem

00:29:28.440 --> 00:29:29.560
and lure her into this trap.

00:30:15.880 --> 00:30:16.880
Calm down.

00:30:18.760 --> 00:30:20.120
Let your instincts guide you.

00:30:21.760 --> 00:30:22.960
I'm right here with you.

00:31:28.360 --> 00:31:29.720
You're lucky you can't see ghosts.

00:31:33.280 --> 00:31:34.480
I don't think so.

00:31:35.280 --> 00:31:37.080
Either way,
that car's trying to run us over.

00:32:21.320 --> 00:32:22.040
Shit...

00:32:22.080 --> 00:32:23.280
Hold tight, Jet.

00:32:30.720 --> 00:32:31.840
They're still here.

00:32:47.280 --> 00:32:48.080
Charn, stop!

00:32:57.960 --> 00:32:59.240
What's going on?

00:32:59.760 --> 00:33:01.640
Why don't they...

00:33:44.640 --> 00:33:45.520
Shit...

00:33:58.280 --> 00:33:59.720
She's here, isn't she?

00:34:12.880 --> 00:34:13.800
Hold on.

00:34:25.239 --> 00:34:26.440
I need a moment.

00:34:33.679 --> 00:34:37.480
If you think
those sacred rice grains will save you,

00:34:38.719 --> 00:34:40.320
I'm warning you.

00:34:40.719 --> 00:34:44.199
They'll only make your death
even more painful.

00:35:01.760 --> 00:35:03.200
So...

00:35:03.240 --> 00:35:06.120
that's all that shaman
could come up with?

00:35:08.980 --> 00:35:11.600
I expected he'd have something better.

00:35:12.960 --> 00:35:14.600
Don't you dare insult my master,

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:15.880
you witch!

00:35:19.960 --> 00:35:21.040
Witch?

00:35:26.560 --> 00:35:28.560
I am no witch.

00:35:29.440 --> 00:35:30.440
That's not what I meant.

00:35:31.040 --> 00:35:31.920
It was a curse.

00:35:33.240 --> 00:35:34.240
Shit!

00:35:34.280 --> 00:35:35.280
What happened?

