You said...

00:39:03.960 --> 00:39:06.040
we'd make it out together, remember?

00:39:07.320 --> 00:39:08.320
Jet,

00:39:08.500 --> 00:39:09.800
please wake up.

00:39:14.060 --> 00:39:15.140
Please...

00:39:39.560 --> 00:39:40.440
Jet...

00:39:40.460 --> 00:39:42.460
Khemjira...

00:40:01.720 --> 00:40:02.600
Together.

00:40:17.720 --> 00:40:22.020
Khemjira...

00:40:26.480 --> 00:40:28.720
You are exceedingly bold to deceive me.

00:41:38.510 --> 00:41:40.470
If you keep fooling around with me,

00:41:41.270 --> 00:41:43.470
you'll miss your chance
to get to your target.

00:41:54.010 --> 00:41:55.310
All set.

00:41:55.350 --> 00:41:57.470
I've had my butler
get the private jet ready.

00:41:58.050 --> 00:42:00.790
We'll take off
as soon as we reach the airport.

00:42:02.950 --> 00:42:04.910
I even told you to get a different car,

00:42:05.580 --> 00:42:07.460
yet you brought another two-seater.

00:42:09.270 --> 00:42:10.630
Come on,

00:42:10.670 --> 00:42:11.910
this is just perfect.

00:42:11.950 --> 00:42:13.070
Cozy, you know?

00:42:26.190 --> 00:42:27.190
Are you tired?

00:42:29.070 --> 00:42:30.070
I'm not.

00:42:31.630 --> 00:42:32.710
I'm worried that I'm too heavy.

00:42:36.190 --> 00:42:37.190
Not at all.

00:42:41.830 --> 00:42:43.030
Keep your eyes on the road.

00:42:44.770 --> 00:42:45.770
Yeah, yeah.

00:42:56.750 --> 00:42:58.550
Luang Por Derm's yantra

00:43:00.230 --> 00:43:02.190
perfectly hides all traces of your soul,

00:43:05.390 --> 00:43:07.190
so Ramphueng's not after us.

00:43:15.590 --> 00:43:16.590
Don't worry.

00:43:18.110 --> 00:43:19.630
From here to the destination,

00:43:21.270 --> 00:43:22.830
you'll be completely safe.

00:43:24.790 --> 00:43:27.150
That means she's definitely after Jet.

00:43:32.830 --> 00:43:34.110
He may not seem serious,

00:43:35.010 --> 00:43:36.410
but when he needs to be,

00:43:36.910 --> 00:43:38.910
he's actually pretty strong.

00:43:43.070 --> 00:43:44.550
I know he's strong,

00:43:45.990 --> 00:43:48.150
but I'm afraid
he might push himself too hard.

00:43:52.630 --> 00:43:54.110
Just remember,

00:43:54.970 --> 00:43:57.190
he is not facing this alone.

00:45:32.470 --> 00:45:33.390
Da?

00:45:33.870 --> 00:45:34.750
Jin...

00:45:45.910 --> 00:45:46.830
Da,

00:45:47.350 --> 00:45:48.590
how did you get here?

00:45:51.550 --> 00:45:53.270
Your friend snuck me in.

00:45:53.630 --> 00:45:55.030
I don't have much time

00:45:55.190 --> 00:45:56.830
before your mom comes.

00:45:58.110 --> 00:45:59.110
Da,

00:45:59.970 --> 00:46:01.190
I'm sorry.

00:46:02.070 --> 00:46:03.350
I'm really sorry.

00:46:05.270 --> 00:46:06.990
Why would you be?

00:46:07.790 --> 00:46:09.790
You've done nothing wrong.

00:46:12.750 --> 00:46:14.270
I thought

00:46:14.550 --> 00:46:16.150
my mom would understand

00:46:16.830 --> 00:46:18.710
and let me come with you.

00:46:22.510 --> 00:46:24.110
It's okay, Jin.

00:46:24.950 --> 00:46:26.150
It's totally okay.

00:46:31.850 --> 00:46:33.430
I'm leaving today.

00:46:38.470 --> 00:46:40.190
I'm really sorry,

00:46:41.070 --> 00:46:43.790
but I can't bear
seeing you marry someone else.

00:46:46.110 --> 00:46:47.670
I'm coming with you, then.

00:46:48.250 --> 00:46:49.830
Right now, just us two.

00:46:52.950 --> 00:46:54.230
What about your wedding

00:46:54.750 --> 00:46:56.350
and your parents?

00:46:57.710 --> 00:46:59.190
You can't do that, Jin.

00:47:09.390 --> 00:47:11.190
You look so gorgeous

00:47:12.070 --> 00:47:13.470
in your wedding dress.

00:47:20.190 --> 00:47:21.550
I'm sorry

00:47:22.550 --> 00:47:24.550
I can't be by your side today.

00:47:45.470 --> 00:47:46.470
Da,

00:47:48.530 --> 00:47:50.110
do you think

00:47:51.430 --> 00:47:53.990
there's a world

00:47:54.910 --> 00:47:59.110
where people of the same gender
can get married?

00:48:01.630 --> 00:48:03.310
You're dreaming again.

00:48:04.190 --> 00:48:06.110
That kind of world doesn't exist.

00:48:08.710 --> 00:48:11.310
But even if we can't get married,

00:48:12.370 --> 00:48:15.150
you'll always be the one I love

00:48:16.350 --> 00:48:18.150
in this life

00:48:18.190 --> 00:48:19.990
or any other.

00:48:21.470 --> 00:48:22.470
Da,

00:48:23.430 --> 00:48:25.030
but I believe

00:48:25.630 --> 00:48:27.110
such a world exists.

00:48:28.430 --> 00:48:30.110
I don't know where,

00:48:31.910 --> 00:48:33.350
but someday,

00:48:34.710 --> 00:48:36.870
we'll meet again

00:48:38.990 --> 00:48:41.190
in a world where we can get married

00:48:42.870 --> 00:48:44.190
and...

00:48:44.910 --> 00:48:46.910
be together forever.

00:48:48.830 --> 00:48:49.950
Because you're the only one

00:48:51.150 --> 00:48:53.750
my heart belongs to

00:48:54.710 --> 00:48:56.590
in this life

00:48:57.430 --> 00:48:59.230
and every life to come.

