♫No more will I let your hand go,♫

00:50:17.950 --> 00:50:20.710
♫Through dream or dawn,
our bond will grow♫

00:50:20.750 --> 00:50:25.030
♫With our two souls,♫

00:50:25.070 --> 00:50:28.710
♫No ending shall this love ever know♫

00:50:28.750 --> 00:50:32.510
♫If I could wish upon a star so bright,♫

00:50:32.550 --> 00:50:37.710
♫I'd ask that we survive
each storm and night♫

00:50:38.110 --> 00:50:45.910
♫While I hold your hand tight
until the end of light♫

