At midnight,
I'll strike the gong to let you know.

00:54:48.510 --> 00:54:49.630
Thanks a lot.

00:54:51.550 --> 00:54:52.990
I hope you stay safe, Khem.

00:54:54.290 --> 00:54:55.940
I'll be waiting
to wish you a happy birthday.

00:54:57.510 --> 00:54:58.790
Thank you, Kachen.

00:56:14.490 --> 00:56:17.410
If you are to use it, think carefully,

00:56:17.930 --> 00:56:19.590
for it carries

00:56:20.050 --> 00:56:22.310
the power of the sacred weapon,

00:56:22.670 --> 00:56:25.070
belonging to the guardian
of the Underworld treasures.

00:56:26.110 --> 00:56:27.870
The human body you inhabit

00:56:27.910 --> 00:56:29.510
is not meant to endure such might.

00:56:31.790 --> 00:56:34.230
Is that the weapon
Lord of the Mountains gave you?

00:56:36.670 --> 00:56:37.550
Yeah.

00:56:39.350 --> 00:56:40.350
Just in case.

00:56:44.070 --> 00:56:45.830
I hope I won't need it.

00:57:00.630 --> 00:57:02.390
She is almost here.

00:57:15.310 --> 00:57:17.990
Keep yourself inside the sacred ring
with Monk Kasem.

00:57:20.190 --> 00:57:21.950
No matter what happens,

00:57:22.990 --> 00:57:25.270
do not leave the ring.

00:57:29.350 --> 00:57:30.870
In a few hours,

00:57:33.150 --> 00:57:35.150
we'll celebrate your birthday together.

00:59:37.190 --> 00:59:39.190
Here I am.

01:00:31.650 --> 01:00:32.650
A monk?

01:00:34.990 --> 01:00:36.190
I see.

01:00:39.910 --> 01:00:41.190
Venerable,

01:00:42.190 --> 01:00:44.910
this is no concern of yours.

01:00:46.590 --> 01:00:50.390
Leave now before my patience withers.

01:01:23.470 --> 01:01:24.910
You damn shaman...

01:01:25.390 --> 01:01:28.470
You never fail to cause me trouble.

01:01:29.910 --> 01:01:31.190
You've lost.

01:01:34.110 --> 01:01:35.630
Now go atone for what you've done.

01:01:37.470 --> 01:01:39.070
What makes you think

01:01:39.270 --> 01:01:41.270
I'd ever lose to you?

01:01:44.910 --> 01:01:48.510
You should've realized it
when you came here alone.

01:01:53.150 --> 01:01:55.950
I've freed every spirit in this place.

01:02:00.110 --> 01:02:02.910
There are no wandering souls left
for you to command.

01:02:04.430 --> 01:02:06.670
Even if you call upon those from afar,

01:02:08.350 --> 01:02:09.510
they won't reach you in time.

01:02:11.710 --> 01:02:13.510
Then...

01:02:14.310 --> 01:02:17.270
face me alone.

01:02:28.630 --> 01:02:31.010
Do you think your invisibility spell

01:02:31.050 --> 01:02:32.990
can save you?

01:02:34.030 --> 01:02:35.630
Who knows?

01:02:35.990 --> 01:02:38.790
But the clock is ticking.

01:02:41.750 --> 01:02:43.350
Show yourself.

01:03:26.670 --> 01:03:28.990
I don't have time for your nonsense.

01:03:54.670 --> 01:03:56.190
A relentless spirit like you

01:03:57.230 --> 01:04:00.150
cannot stand against
Phraya Ananta Nagaraja's might.

01:04:02.190 --> 01:04:04.390
I bet Phraya Ananta Nagaraja...

01:04:05.150 --> 01:04:07.950
can't even keep you breathing, can he?

01:04:19.140 --> 01:04:20.340
Master!

01:04:50.310 --> 01:04:51.910
I granted you a chance,

01:04:52.990 --> 01:04:54.910
but since you insist on opposing me,

01:04:55.710 --> 01:04:56.750
then die.

01:05:48.510 --> 01:05:49.910
It's past midnight.

01:05:51.390 --> 01:05:53.390
Khem's 21 now.

01:05:54.470 --> 01:05:55.470
Let him go.

01:05:57.070 --> 01:05:59.190
And why should I do that?

01:06:02.710 --> 01:06:05.230
If you break the vow you swore,

01:06:06.950 --> 01:06:08.910
your soul will fade away.

01:06:10.150 --> 01:06:12.470
The vow I swore?

01:06:14.790 --> 01:06:15.990
Ramphueng,

01:06:17.910 --> 01:06:20.310
I understand
losing your son must've hurt deeply,

01:06:24.430 --> 01:06:26.750
but I have nothing to do with it.

01:06:28.590 --> 01:06:30.790
Let's finally set each other free.

01:06:33.630 --> 01:06:34.630
No.

01:06:35.830 --> 01:06:37.430
This can't be the end.

01:06:41.830 --> 01:06:43.070
It's over.

01:06:45.110 --> 01:06:46.990
Go and face your karma.

01:07:05.350 --> 01:07:06.830
They're finally here.

01:07:43.190 --> 01:07:44.990
You may not know

01:07:47.250 --> 01:07:49.030
that a place not far from here

01:07:49.430 --> 01:07:51.430
was once a battlefield,

01:07:52.430 --> 01:07:56.230
filled with spirits
I could bind to serve me.

01:08:01.750 --> 01:08:03.550
And you probably didn't know

01:08:04.830 --> 01:08:06.630
when I said

01:08:06.670 --> 01:08:09.750
Khem must die at 21,

01:08:14.230 --> 01:08:17.229
I never said it had to be at midnight.

01:08:19.310 --> 01:08:22.510
He was born at six in the morning.

01:08:33.670 --> 01:08:34.670
Peem!

01:09:04.069 --> 01:09:05.710
I can sense that Khem's still alive,

01:09:05.750 --> 01:09:07.149
but that doesn't mean he's safe.

01:09:08.830 --> 01:09:09.950
Please stop.

01:09:10.990 --> 01:09:13.270
My life is all you want, right?

01:09:13.550 --> 01:09:14.390
Khem...

01:09:14.870 --> 01:09:15.990
Go back!

01:09:16.229 --> 01:09:18.229
In my past life,

01:09:19.590 --> 01:09:22.390
I let someone die right before my eyes.

01:09:23.069 --> 01:09:25.790
You will know the pain I've felt.

01:09:26.270 --> 01:09:27.390
Goodbye.

01:09:32.630 --> 01:09:35.729
♫It's more than love at first sight,♫

01:09:35.770 --> 01:09:37.870
♫But a bond through every life♫

01:09:37.910 --> 01:09:41.490
♫Our destinies cross again in this life♫

01:09:41.529 --> 01:09:44.490
♫You'll be my last, my eternal light,♫

01:09:44.529 --> 01:09:46.600
♫From now until the end of time♫

01:09:50.330 --> 01:09:53.279
♫Whether it's a dream or it's true,♫

01:09:53.319 --> 01:09:55.670
♫My heart forever stays with you♫

01:09:55.710 --> 01:09:59.080
♫No force shall tear our souls in two♫

01:09:59.120 --> 01:10:02.120
♫I love you through and through♫

01:10:02.350 --> 01:10:04.530
♫Even if the world ceases to move,♫

01:10:04.570 --> 01:10:07.870
♫These words will still be true,♫

01:10:07.910 --> 01:10:13.310
♫I love you♫